The paper deals with facial recognition models and privacy protection, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and security and privacy (cs.CR) categories. The paper proposes a new system, Fawkes, which involves deep learning models, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of algorithms to protect personal privacy, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category.
